=== Internals Micro-Benchmark ===
node      : v24.14.0
platform  : linux x64
warmup    : 5  rounds: 12  batch: 5000

--- encode(): circular-ref check overhead ---
  encode (with circ-check) x5000             median=2.2 µs p95=2.9 µs 461.1 K ops/s
  encode (skip circ-check) x5000             median=1.8 µs p95=6.3 µs 545.9 K ops/s
  overhead: +18.4% (circ-check vs skip)

--- registry lookup: LRU vs unlimited ---
  getByFingerprint (unlimited) x5000         median=372 ns p95=2.2 µs 2.69 M ops/s
  getByFingerprint (maxSize=200) x5000       median=505 ns p95=1.7 µs 1.98 M ops/s
  LRU overhead: +35.7%

--- fingerprint: canonical form vs JSON.stringify ---
  fingerprint (canonical) x5000              median=22.9 µs p95=45.9 µs 43.7 K ops/s
  fingerprint (JSON.stringify) x5000         median=15.3 µs p95=50.5 µs 65.3 K ops/s
  canonical overhead: +49.6% (one-time cost at schema registration)

=== Summary ===
circ-check overhead on encode : +18.4%
LRU bookkeeping overhead      : +35.7%
canonical form overhead       : +49.6% (registration-time only, not hot path)

